<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>
<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code><code><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/CSS_values_syntax#syntax-single-animation-play-state" title="running | paused">&lt;single-animation-play-state&gt;</a><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#Hash_mark_(.23)" title="Hash mark multiplier: the previous entity may appear 0, 1 or several times, each occurence being separated from the previous one by a comma">#</a></code></code>
</pre>
<pre>animation-play-state: running
animation-play-state: paused

animation-play-state: paused, running, running
</pre>
<h3 id="Values">Values</h3>
<dl><dt>
  <code>running</code></dt>
 <dd>
  The animation is currently playing.</dd>
 <dt>
  <code>paused</code></dt>
 <dd>
  The animation is currently paused.</dd>
</dl>